headline: Federal firings, economic uncertainty stain REIT outlooks
summary: Equity Residential CEO Mark Parrell, AvalonBay CEO Sean Breslin and Camden Property Trust CEO Ric Campo (Getty, Equity Residential, AvalonBay, Federal Reserve Bank of Dallas)The heads of the country’s largest apartment REITs are finally giving their two cents on how tariffs, trade wars and economic tumult might affect business. An outlook during earnings season should be par for the course. […]This article originally appeared on The Real Deal. Click here to read the full story.

headline: EQR hits all-time low for turnover
summary: The 7.9% rate was due in part to the Chicago-based REIT’s centralized renewal process, according to COO Michael Manelis.
